From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tyson Trautmann <tysont@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 11:00:00 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Return readdirplus directory stats

Fetch the directory and parent attributes alongside its entries so FUSE
readdirplus can fill the "." and ".." rows without extra getattr calls. Add a
default FileSystem::readdir_plus_with_directory_stats built on the existing
primitives, override it in AgentFS with a single CTE, forward it
through the mount adapter, and consume the enriched listing in the FUSE
readdirplus handler.
---
